{
  "stem": "27507.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were putting-- they were dressing in-- they usually were wearing high leather boots and some kind of a fairly smart coat and a belt.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They looked quite smart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And in the beginning, they had all kinds of duties, but they were not horrible.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But of course, quite soon after, they were being used for all kinds of duties which were much more doubtful, like they had, for example, to catch people for labor camps, for labor duties.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And some might have left and-- and not-- and not-- not gone along with it, but some have continued very well.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the commanders of the Jewish police were cooperating more and more with the Germans, and were-- in the end became completely German agents.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So it was-- I would say that the whole of the Jewish police in the end, or most of it, were-- as far as their moral position is concerned, it was, I would say, very doubtful, very, very questionable.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And in the end, it was-- absolutely in the end when there was a liquidation, it was completely horrible.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the-- the hunger, particularly in this first winter, but even all the time after, I think, was something that was not even a day to day, but it was a most obvious occurrence so that one became terribly used to it in the end because people were hungry.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were masses and masses of people who were hungry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were beggars everywhere, particularly in the main streets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were beggars sitting at the side of the pavement, the beggars sitting next to the gutter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The beggars were-- in the main streets, there were many of them, and-- although I avoided those main streets because they were crowded, and they were horrible.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
